- [ ] `governance/executable/workflows/consumer-alignment.yml.template` produces `governance-layer-down-intake.yml` (agent-intake pattern, no auto-PR)
- [ ] All legacy workflows listed above are deleted
- [ ] `.github/workflows/README.md` is updated and accurate
